Usage: write_path_list_summary [-help] [-category <string>] [-compress] [-csv]
                               -report <string>

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-category <string>   # Specifies the category of paths to write to the csv
                     # file. (string, optional)
-compress            # gzip output report. (bool, optional)
-csv                 # Reports entries in csv format. (bool, optional)
-report <string>     # Specifies the name of the csv output file.
                     # (string, required)